            <lg xml:id="TK1322">
<l>ūṭaliṟ ṟōṉṟuñ ciṟutuṉi nallaḷi</l>
<l> vāṭiṉum pāṭu peṟum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>His love will increase though it may (at first seem to) fade through the short-lived distress caused by (my) dislike.</l>
